Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Big Bear Mountain
Description: A wonderful mountain located in California that has a ski resort, many outdoor activties and lots of snow!

Name: Las Vegas Strip
Description: The most iconic street in Las Vegas for its flashy and luxurious casinos, hotels, and stores that you view as you walk down the street.

Name: Golden Gate Bridge
Description: Located in San Francisco, CA and is iconic for it's massive scale and astonishing detail for a bridge.

Name: Mount Rushmore
Description: Located in South Dakota, is an enormous mountain carved into four of our founding fathers surrounded by a beautiful national forest.

Name: Eiffel Tower
Description: One of the tallest statues known for it's unique triangular design located in Paris, France and was built in 1889.
